data.title: Prince Vault
data.text:
All Songs known to have writing input by Prince (including songs recorded by Prince in the studio).

Definition

This list includes all songs known to be written by Prince (regardless of official credits, and/or whether a studio recording is known to exist). Recording information on songs is not always available, or not accurate enough to state a specific year of recording. In this case, the year will be followed by a *.

This list purposely doesn’t include the following categories of songs, which are not reputed as having writing or co-writing credits by Prince:

songs known to contain a Prince participation as a musician and/or producer only, example: After Hi School;

studio recorded covers or released rehearsal covers of another artist’s song by Prince, example: A Case Of U or Crimson And Clover;

remixes of another artist’s song by Prince, example: Lolly Lolly.

A list of these songs can be found on the Contribution and Cover songs page.

A list of only the (known) Prince-penned song titles that remain unreleased can be found here: Unreleased Songs.
